ng>NavigatorPlugins</strong></code> interface contains methods and properties related to the plugins installed in the browser.</p>\n\n<p>There is no object of type <code>NavigatorPlugins</code>, but other interfaces, like <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a>, implement it.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"navigatorplugins.mimetypes\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/orphaned/Web/API/NavigatorPlugins/mimeTypes\"><code>NavigatorPlugins.mimeTypes</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns an <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MimeTypeArray\"><code>MimeTypeArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> listing the MIME types supported by the browser.</dd>\n <dt id=\"navigatorplugins.plugins\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/orphaned/Web/API/NavigatorPlugins/plugins\"><code>NavigatorPlugins.plugins</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> listing the plugins installed in the browser.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>The <code>NavigatorPlugins</code></em><em> interface doesn't inherit any method.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"navigatorplugins.javaenabled\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/orphaned/Web/API/NavigatorPlugins/javaEnabled\"><code>NavigatorPlugins.javaEnabled</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> flag indicating whether the host browser is Java-enabled or not.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#navigatorplugins\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'NavigatorPlugins' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Browser compatibility","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Pulpit</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>The <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a> interface that implements it.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The NavigatorPlugins interface contains methods and properties related to the plugins installed in the browser.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"NavigatorPlugins","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"NavigatorPlugins","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/orphaned/web/api/navigatorplugins","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/orphaned/web/api/navigatorplugins/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"NavigatorPlugins | MDN","noIndexing":true}}